and that's barely two-thirds of all projects.

5
00:00:12.927 --> 00:00:13.329
Good,

6
00:00:13.329 --> 00:00:16.351
quality project work management will help you better succeed

7
00:00:16.351 --> 00:00:17.967
at running and completing your projects.

8
00:00:17.967 --> 00:00:20.957
The Project Management Office (PMO),

9
00:00:20.957 --> 00:00:25.584
we explored why it is important to have a PMO to help manage project

10
00:00:25.584 --> 00:00:28.796
demand and execute projects following standards and metrics and

11
